	.string "So it's {PLAYER}{KUN}?$"

gText_Birch_YourePlayer::
	.string "Ah, okay!\p"
	.string "You're {PLAYER}{KUN} who lives in\n"
	.string "my town of residence: {COLOR BLUE}Pearl Town{COLOR DARK_GRAY}.\l"
	.string "I've heard of you from your mom!\p"
	.string "$"

gText_Birch_AreYouReady::
	.string "All right, are you ready?\p"
	.string "Your very own adventure is about\n"
	.string "to unfold!\p"
	.string "Take courage, and leap into this\n"
	.string "new world of Pokémon where dreams\l"
	.string "become reality!\p"
	.string "Come visit me in my Pokémon Lab\n"
	.string "when you wake up.\p"
	.string "$"
